hes guide Current stories.", "imagename": "2dda8693-e90f-46aa-bbd9-abff2cd822af.gif", "infoid": 1019, "category": "technology_Google", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["google", "current"]}, {"url": "http://www.liweiart.com/ART/liwei/PHOTO.htm/PHOTO0000.htm", "title": "\u674e\u4f1f\u7684\u8da3\u5473\u56fe\u7247", "tags": "\u674e\u4f1f \u8da3\u5473\u56fe\u7247 ", "name": "huipk", "posttime": "2006-02-25 15:28:19", "ip": "61.135.146.228", "mark": 18, "note": "\u4f60\u4e5f\u8bb8\u4e0d\u77e5\u9053\u674e\u4f1f\u662f\u8c01\uff1f\r\n\u4f46\u4f60\u4e00\u5b9a\u5728\u7f51\u4e0a\u89c1\u8fc7\u8fd9\u6837\u7684\u56fe\u7247.\r\n\u6709\u70b9\u521b\u610f\u597d\u561b?\u6765\u7b11\u4e00\u4e2a", "imagename": "4dfad97c-a031-4a31-a01e-795f99d9ee5f.jpg", "infoid": 1018, "category": "technology_design", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["\u674e\u4f1f", "\u8da3\u5473\u56fe\u7247"]}, {"url": "http://www.brookstone.com/shop/product.asp?product_code=IPILLOW&world_code=2&category_code=20&subcat", "title": "Brookstone.com : iPillow\u2122 - iPod\u6795\u5934\u97f3\u54cd", "tags": "iPod \u6795\u5934 \u97f3\u54cd iPillow ", "name": "pica", "posttime": "2006-02-25 14:59:41", "ip": "218.28.177.3", "mark": 3, "note": "\u771f\u5b9e\u4ee4\u4eba\u60ca\u5947\u7684\u6770\u4f5c\uff0c\u5b89\u8be6\u5730\u8eba\u5728\u8fd9\u6837\u7684\u6795\u5934\u4e0a\uff0c\u8046\u542c\u7740\u4f18\u7f8e\u7684\u97f3\u4e50\u3002Simply plug in your MP3 player and listen to your favorite tunes. Our pillow speaker contains two built-in speakers, but with a visco-elastic foam interior and plush micro-suede exterior, it also the perfect place to cradle your neck.", "imagename": "abb530f4-f3cb-47ce-b7dc-049f187e4b90.jpg", "infoid": 1016, "category": "technology_gadgets", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["ipod", "\u6795\u5934", "\u97f3\u54cd", "ipillow"]}, {"url": "http://uncyclopedia.org/wiki/Microsoft", "title": "Wikipedia\u6076\u641e\u7248", "tags": "Wikipedia \u6076\u641e Microsoft ", "name": "geekzhang", "posttime": "2006-02-25 12:32:19", "ip": "218.28.177.3", "mark": 9, "note": "\u6709\u610f\u601d\uff0c\u6211\u5728\u91cc\u9762\u7279\u5730\u67e5\u8be2\u4e86\u4e00\u4e0bMicrosoft,\u679c\u7136,\u5bf9\u8fd9\u4e2a\u8f6f\u4ef6\u516c\u53f8\u8fdb\u884c\u4e86\u6781\u5ea6\u5938\u5f20\u5f0f\u5730\u8bbd\u523a\u6076\u641e\u3002\u7279\u7ecf\u5178\u7684\u5c31\u662f\u90a3\u4e2a\u201c\u5e7f\u544a\u56fe\u7247\u201d:if you dot'st buy windows Vista,we'll kill this dog.", "imagename": "98ca6629-0c02-4eee-91c8-61b1f8f62e69.jpg", "infoid": 1014, "category": "technology_web2", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["wikipedia", "\u6076\u641e", "microsoft"]}, {"url": "http://www.thetechzone.com/chiller.php", "title": "USB\u996e\u6599\u51b7\u5374\u5668", "tags": "USB \u996e\u6599 \u51b7\u5374\u5668 ", "name": "geekzhang", "posttime": "2006-02-25 12:12:48", "ip": "218.28.177.3", "mark": 3, "note": "We all know that USB is very versatile and can be used for anything from transferring data to powering a laptop light. However, this is the first time we've seen USB used for keeping your drink cold. The CoolIT USB Beverage Chiller is, as far as we know, the world's first USB powered drink cooler. CoolIT Systems, the makers of the Chiller, claims this is the next must-have computer accessory. With the USB Beverage Chiller at your side, you can keep your beverage chilled and stay at your computer longer.", "imagename": "12745390-e01f-4da3-82f6-948f42d52317.jpg", "infoid": 1013, "category": "technology_hardware", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["usb", "\u996e\u6599", "\u51b7\u5374\u5668"]}, {"url": "http://reviews.designtechnica.com/guide46.html", "title": "The 2006 Best of Web 2.0  - Designtechnica", "tags": "2006 Web 2.0 Best ", "name": "geekzhang", "posttime": "2006-02-25 12:09:35", "ip": "218.28.177.3", "mark": 3, "note": "The next generation of the web is here! With new kinds of desktop-like applications being released left and right, how will you know where to go and what to use? That\u2019s why we\u2019re here: To show you the best of Web 2.0 sites that you can get the most out of. No matter the task, video, audio, or photos, we have a site that works great for what you want to do and uses all the great features of Web 2.0 technology.", "imagename": "b50f12bf-eed5-4838-b407-fb19545989d3.jpg", "infoid": 1012, "category": "technology_web2", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["2006", "web", "2.0", "best"]}, {"url": "http://www.flickr.com/photos/brettlider/sets/154249", "title": "Google Food Photo Blog", "tags": "Google Food Photo Blog flickr \u98df\u7269 ", "name": "geekzhang", "posttime": "2006-02-25 12:04:29", "ip": "218.28.177.3", "mark": 3, "note": "Google\u7684\u5458\u5de5\u90fd\u5403\u54ea\u4e9b\u7f8e\u5473\u53ef\u53e3\u7684\u98df\u7269\u5462\uff1f\u770b\u770b\u8fd9\u4e2aGoogle Food Photo Blog on flickr.", "imagename": "739ecb3c-9245-4c28-a5f5-6886d3482999.jpg", "infoid": 1011, "category": "technology_Google", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["google", "food", "photo", "blog", "flickr", "\u98df\u7269"]}, {"url": "http://odeo.com", "title": "\u514d\u8d39\u7684\u8bed\u97f3\u4fe1\u7bb1", "tags": "Odeo \u8bed\u97f3\u7559\u8a00 web 2.0 ", "name": "kevinnet", "posttime": "2006-02-25 02:18:41", "ip": "220.248.152.155", "mark": 6, "note": "Odeo is a small company based in San Francisco, California.\r\n\u53ef\u4ee5\u5efa\u7acb\u81ea\u5df1\u7684\u9891\u9053,\u6709\u70b9\u50cf\u64ad\u5ba2\r\n\u4e3b\u8981\u529f\u80fd\u662f\u8bed\u97f3\u7559\u8a00.", "imagename": "c7505fe8-80ef-4443-9d69-a6